    text: "Welding reels are mesmerising — the arc glowing, the weld pool rippling, filler rod feeding, sparks cascading. And the reveal of a finished stainless balustrade or a polished handrail generates DMs from people wanting the same craftsmanship applied to their own projects."
  },
  {
    icon: '🎯',
    title: 'Reaches Design-Led Clients',
    text: "Instagram attracts homeowners, architects, and designers who value aesthetics. A DM saying 'the staircase in your latest post is exactly what we want — can you make something similar?' is a pre-qualified commission from someone who already appreciates your fabrication quality."
  },
  {
    icon: '📱',
    title: 'Handles Visual Reference DMs',
    text: "Followers DM with screenshots, sketches, and design references — 'can you make something like this but in stainless instead of mild steel?' The AI asks about dimensions, location, and finish, converting visual inspiration into a structured fabrication brief."
  },
  {
    icon: '🌙',
    title: 'Captures Late-Night Design Planning',
    text: "Homeowners plan metalwork projects after dinner — scrolling fabrication portfolios, saving design ideas, and messaging workshops at 11pm. The AI captures every late-night design conversation."
  },
  {
    icon: '📋',
    title: 'Structures Aspirational DMs',
