  }
];

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What Instagram account type do I need?",
    answer: "Switch to a Business or Creator profile through your Instagram settings — it is a free change that takes under two minutes. Link it to your Facebook page for full integration. Fabrication workshops showcasing welding reels, workshop progress, and installed project carousels benefit from the professional analytics and promoted post tools that a Business account unlocks."
  },
  {
    question: "What metalwork DMs arrive through Instagram?",
    answer: "Design-conscious homeowners, architects, and interior designers. Typical DMs include 'love the balustrade in your gallery — can you quote for something similar?', 'how much for a pair of contemporary gates?', and 'we need a fabricator for a feature staircase — can you design and build one?' These enquiries carry strong conversion potential because the sender has already reviewed your visual portfolio."
  },
  {
    question: "How fast does the AI reply to fabrication DMs?",
    answer: "The response appears within seconds of the DM arriving. Instagram read indicators show your workshop responding immediately. Design-led clients who DM multiple fabricators simultaneously typically select the workshop that responds first with an informed question about their specific material preferences, dimensions, or design direction."
  },
  {
    question: "What does Instagram DMs cost for fabrication workshops?",
    answer: `Instagram DMs is £${pricing.addOn.price}/month as a channel add-on. Fabrication workshops with compelling visual portfolios — showing polished welds, dramatic installations, and bespoke designs — attract high-value commissions. A single staircase or gate package secured through a prompt Instagram DM typically ranges from £3,000 to £30,000.`
  },
  {
    question: "Can I reply to DMs personally?",
    answer: "Send a single message in any DM thread and the AI transfers control to you permanently. Most fabricators let the AI gather the initial scope — metalwork type, material preference, key dimensions, finish, installation location — then follow up personally to share design concepts, discuss construction methodology, and book the site survey."
  },
  {
    question: "Is DM data from metalwork queries handled securely?",
    answer: "All Instagram DM content — design references, property photographs, project dimensions, material preferences, and contact information — is encrypted and stored on UK and EU servers under UK GDPR. No data is shared with competing fabricators, used for advertising, or disclosed to any third party."
